txt.en: For many ages, the Earth-kin protected the pass through Ram Dúath from Angmar, but since the betrayal of the Suuri-lehmä tribe by First Hunter Jarkko and his followers, the Earth-kin have themselves become trapped in the North Downs.

For many ages, the Earth-kin protected the pass through Ram Dúath from Angmar, but since the betrayal of the Suuri-lehmä tribe by First Hunter Jarkko and his followers, the Earth-kin have themselves become trapped in the North Downs.\n\nYou should defeat the Rauta-lehmä, as the traitors call themselves. Show them that their betrayal is known and will not be brooked.
The Earth-kin of the Rauta-lehmä faction are encamped east of Esteldín in Nan Amlug.\n\nYou should show the traitorous Rauta-lehmä that they have chosen the wrong side in the coming war.
You have defeated a number of the Rauta-lehmä in eastern Nan Amlug.
You have defeated the Earth-kin of the Rauta-lehmä in the eastern section of Nan Amlug.
'The Earth-kin, despite their strange aspect, have always been a peace-loving people, until the betrayal of the Rauta-Lehmä. The traitors have little regard for life.'
'If you are willing, speak with Elúr. He may need your assistance with a task I have burdened him with.'
